{"tid":1680631,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【最緊要正字】不要再『黃色乜乜乜』了好嘛？","createTime":"2019-10-29T02:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T04:50:09.000Z","uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d20f556a61bb4c5a3fcb8d3731a39c156a4f57","tid":1680631,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"見有人呢排提倡緊「黃色生活圈」，「黃色經濟圈」咁，其實我對個名呢就有啲意見。<br />\n<br />\n強烈建議不要稱「黃色乜乜乜」，眾所周知，喺廣東話來講黃色有色情嘅意味，就如「黃色笑話」，「黃色電影」。你想大家提倡嘅嘢以後同色情混為一談嘛？<br />\n其實調一調，改少少字，叫「黃絲乜乜乜」「黃的乜乜乜」「黃系乜乜乜」或直接「黃乜乜乜」也可以呢？<br />\n<br />\n匪共就係將「信仰」變「迷信」，「官廷」變「反共」，先至變成大惡人。<br />\n<br />\n要文化傳承恆久，用字就要慬慎，要準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">天滅中共！<br />\n共黨死全家！<br />\n皇天擊殺！<br />\n香港警察！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5c9c30d7711e83834773711ec21e6733bdeb9814","tid":1680631,"uid":6003,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"樓主請收皮<br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得係時候叫停民間記者會？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439342</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f5875dc302c73188c156e9732171cdb848531ed1","tid":1680631,"uid":80763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972f15c8f587780f90d31c939d2ebfa6379bb9ff","tid":1680631,"uid":79314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"樓主請收皮"},{"pid":"dc27eb810f524192a5a1f9a9a828d20570b0ce8c","tid":1680631,"uid":28792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"老一輩將黃色同色情掛勾<br />\n我哋新一代就唔可以將黃色同自由抗爭掛勾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0040c1f161ad59a3571a7da79662a2b9390a86eb","tid":1680631,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}